message.content: cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.FL, cs.ET - This paper deals with testing and conformance between implementation and specification, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. It also mentions the use of finite state machines (FSM), which is a topic in programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses the ioco relation, which is a topic in logic (cs.LO) and formal languages (cs.FL). Finally, the paper proposes a method for test generation, which falls under the category of software testing (cs.ET).
